OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1775146264
OL,3,CThe victims who paid thousands for
OL,4,Cfuneral plans that didn't exist
OL,6,FPeople who paid thousands of pounds
OL,7,Ffor funeral plans that never existed
OL,8,Fsay the con man responsible is
OL,9,F"disgusting".
OL,11,FRobert Bush, who ran Legacy
OL,12,FIndependent Funeral Directors in Hull,
OL,13,Ftook money from multiple victims to
OL,14,Fmake funeral arrangements in the event
OL,15,Fof their death.
OL,17,FHe has now pleaded guilty to more than
OL,18,Fsixty charges, including fraud.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
