OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1775146264
OL,3,CThe victims who paid thousands for
OL,4,Cfuneral plans that didn't exist
OL,6,FYvonne Colby, 85, said she wanted to
OL,7,Ffund her own funeral to remove the
OL,8,Fburden from her family.
OL,10,FShe only found out that the funeral
OL,11,Fplan was bogus after Humberside Police
OL,12,Flaunched an investigation into Legacy
OL,13,Fin 2024.
OL,15,FBy then she had paid about #2,500 in
OL,16,Fcash.
OL,18,F"We're old-fashioned," she said. "We
OL,19,Fdidn't believe in debt and such like.
OL,20,FAnd we always paid in cash. I still
OL,21,Feven now prefer to pay cash for things.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1775146264
OL,3,CThe victims who paid thousands for
OL,4,Cfuneral plans that didn't exist
OL,6,F"It was really a shock to find out
OL,7,Fwhat had happened."
OL,9,FMrs Colby, whose husband had a plan
OL,10,Fwith Legacy which did cover his
OL,11,Ffuneral when he died, said Bush had
OL,12,Fcome across as "honest".
OL,14,FShe said the experience had left her
OL,15,F"wary" of the funerals industry.
OL,17,F"It's made me very sad that we thought
OL,18,Fwe were all organised," she said.
OL,20,F"And now I've got to pay out again.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1775146264
OL,3,CThe victims who paid thousands for
OL,4,Cfuneral plans that didn't exist
OL,6,F"It's just kind of made me think, who
OL,7,Fcan I trust, who can I believe?"
OL,9,F"I's just unbelievable, really, that
OL,10,Fhe's done it. And why has he done it?
OL,11,FFor what reason? I mean, he can't have
OL,12,Fgained anything."
OL,14,FMrs Colby's daughter Michaela Colby-
OL,15,FBrinkley said there were "no words" to
OL,16,Fdescribe what had happened.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1775146264
OL,3,CThe victims who paid thousands for
OL,4,Cfuneral plans that didn't exist
OL,6,FShe said: "It's really, really
OL,7,Ffrustrating that he can steal from
OL,8,Fpeople and he doesn't really care
OL,9,Fbecause he's done it more than once.
OL,10,FAnd that's really, really infuriating.
OL,12,F"He's disgusting, he is just
OL,13,Fdisgusting. I don't know how he can do
OL,14,Fthis to people."
OL,16,FJeffrey Richards and his partner
OL,17,FMaureen had paid #4,200 when they
OL,18,Ffound out their funeral plan did not
OL,19,Fexist.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1775146264
OL,3,CThe victims who paid thousands for
OL,4,Cfuneral plans that didn't exist
OL,6,FHe said he had wanted to avoid his
OL,7,Fchildren facing "hardship" when he
OL,8,Fdied.
OL,10,F"I'm not a man who gets very angry
OL,11,Fhalf the time," he said. "But if I'd
OL,12,Fhave spoken to (Robert Bush), I might
OL,13,Fhave used some harsh words."
OL,15,FMr Richards described Bush as "jovial
OL,16,Fbloke", who was trusted in the
OL,17,Fcommunity.
OL,19,F"Local man and everything," he said.
OL,20,F"Turns out he was the local con man."
OL,26,@tD@PpmtD@\pn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1775146264
OL,3,CThe victims who paid thousands for
OL,4,Cfuneral plans that didn't exist
OL,6,FHe said he had managed to get some of
OL,7,Fthe money back, but the cost of
OL,8,Ffuneral plans had risen sharply in the
OL,9,Fmeantime.
OL,11,F"I'm still financially out of pocket
OL,12,Fbecause the funeral plan I've taken
OL,13,Fout now is nearly double what I took
OL,14,Fout before," he said.
OL,16,FHe advised other people to carry out
OL,17,Fchecks before taking out funeral plans.
OL,19,FAnd, asked what he would say to Robert
OL,20,FBush, he added: "Enjoy your stay at
OL,21,FHer Majesty's Pleasure."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
